Placed my order at 7.12pm. Waited for half an hour and order was still not ready. At 7.55pm, I decided to do my prayers and come back again. Came back at 8.14pm and to my astonishment, order still not ready. Headed to the counter and they immediately prepared my order. Would advised fellow diners not to patronize this outlet during the dinner crowd.
